---
title: Spiced Chicken Schnitzel & Oven-Baked Wedges with Celery Slaw & Garlic Aioli
description: It’s time for another twist on a schnitzel! These tender pieces of chicken breast are coated in a golden crumb with Mumbai spices throughout. We’ve kept the sides simple and classic, because really, how do you compete with wedges and slaw for the perfect schnitzel accompaniments.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66c6a6c7b372008c572c369b-ca35dbcf.jpeg
